### Link to this sectionRun on JetPack 7.0#

#### Link to this sectionInstall Ultralytics Package#

Here we will install Ultralytics package on the Jetson with optional dependencies so that we can export the [PyTorch](https://www.ultralytics.com/glossary/pytorch) models to other different formats. We will mainly focus on [NVIDIA TensorRT exports](/integrations/tensorrt) because TensorRT will make sure we can get the maximum performance out of the Jetson devices.

